window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Reagan Prefontaine anticipates a great week of diving off Tulum while visiting her brother. When he turns up missing, it mobilizes Reaganâ€™s passion to find answers...at all costs.</p> <p>One memorable dive following an unprecedented tropical storm changes the trajectory of her life. Something gold shimmers in the distance. A mackerel? The tank of another diver? What she discovers will weave together the lives of two young girls born centuries apart. </p> <p>The mysterious mark on her arm draws curiosity from some, concern from others, and malicious machinations from organized crime.</p>"; 
